divs: sighting detailsi was in my room getting ready for bed after i worked the nightshift. i wanted to see how my new underwear set looked on me, so i decided to take a picture. after i took the first photo (11\29\2009 11:43 a.m.) i turned my camera around to see and i noticed some weird light patterns that were pretty intricate. so i took another, and this picture was covered in more light patterns. i ended up taking a couple more, and got more interference. when i first took the pictures, i didn't think of aliens at all, i really didn't know what to make of them. i just knew that these weren't the typical light flashes you see in your pictures sometimes, the lines were too detailed. i only came to the idea that it might be alien interference in my pictures after i had a vivid alien dream over a year after i took the pictures. i will only be posting one of these pictures, due to the fact that there is personal images(my face)in the others and i don't want to post them online to the public. i hope to get some feedback to what the photo analyst makes of the picture.
